org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.scoring.impl

Class RegressionScoreFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.scoring.impl.BaseNetScoreFunction
      • org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.scoring.impl.RegressionScoreFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ScoreFunction

    public class RegressionScoreFunction
extends BaseNetScoreFunction
    Score function for regression (including multi-label regression) for a MultiLayerNetwork or ComputationGraph on a test set. Supports all regression metrics: RegressionEvaluation.Metric
    Author:
    Alex Black
